flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Tenancy Detail Page]
    B --> C[Click Serve Section 8 Notice]
    C --> D[Serve Notice Modal Opens]
    D --> E[Select Section 8 Ground]
    E --> F{Ground Type?}
    F -->|Mandatory| G[Mandatory Ground Info Shown]
    F -->|Discretionary| H[Discretionary Ground Info Shown]
    G --> I[View Required Documents]
    H --> I
    I --> J[View Notice Period]
    J --> K[Enter Supporting Details]
    K --> L[Set Date Notice Served]
    L --> M[Earliest Possession Date Calculated]
    M --> N[Read Legal Declaration]
    N --> O{Confirm Declaration?}
    O -->|No| N
    O -->|Yes| P[Click Record Notice Served]
    P --> Q[Notice Saved to Database]
    Q --> R[Status: Notice Served]
    R --> S[Notice Date and Ground Shown on Tenancy]
    S --> T([End])
